data.description: Absolutely AMAZING Taylor Morrison home with STUNNING Mountain Views - the Sunrise Vista community named and noted for exquisite sunrise/sunset views year around! RV PARKING ALLOWED alongside the custom-built (2022) 2 CAR detached garage or west side paved driveway, PLUS 3 CAR garage attached with temperature control.  OASIS backyard is a luxurious paradise, prime for a cool splash and poolside entertainment under solid-roof lighted Pergola and outdoor surround-sound speakers with Sono amp.  Gourmet Kitchen boasts GE Monogram Series appliances with a grand, 7x10' granite center island. (Hard to step away from the central heart of this home!)  Primary en Suite includes ''Super Shower'' with dual rain-shower heads and custom jets for the ultimate in a luxuriating shower experience. Extended-length walk-in closet provides an abundance of closet storage space with added ceiling height!  Primary Suite is split from additional bedrooms. Additional bedroom area includes separate 'BONUS ROOM" as "secondary family room".  Guest bath has been recently upgraded (2022). Extended height walk-in pantry adds that extra-storage, always a PLUS in a designer kitchen!  Double French doors enclose the home office, affording privacy, high ceilings, and front view. Home warranty can be transferred - available through May 2029.  In this premier Taylor Morrison Home Community, Sunrise Vista offers superior high performance features, standard custom attributes and a place you may soon call HOME!
